Cls

Assign AGS: AGS_Drive:AGS2
Assign Scripts: AGS:Scripts
Assign Admin: Scripts:Admin
Assign Emulators: Extra:Emulators
Assign ST-00: Media:ST-00

Assign >NIL: EXISTS SHARED:
IF NOT WARN
 Assign WHDSaves: SHARED:SaveGames
Else
 Assign >NIL: EXISTS SHARE:
 IF NOT WARN
; AGS Expects SHARED:
  Assign SHARED: SHARE:
  IF NOT EXISTS SHARED:SaveGames
   makedir SHARED:SaveGames
  Endif
  Assign WHDSaves: SHARED:SaveGames
 Else
; AGS Expects SHARED: patch to RAM:
  Assign SHARED: RAM:
  makedir RAM:SaveGames
  Assign WHDSaves: RAM:SaveGames
 Endif
Endif

Ex >NIL: Scripts:Speed_Reset
Echo "*e[1m"
Ex Scripts:Splash
Echo ""
Wait 1
Type AGS:Texts/Retro32.txt
Echo ""
Wait 1
Type AGS:Texts/immortal.txt
Echo "*e[0m"
Wait 1
Ex Scripts:Startup_Splash

Ex Scripts:HW_Select

If $HW EQ "Mini"
  Assign AGS_Drive: WHD1:
  Assign AGS_Drive: WHD2: ADD
  Assign AGS_Drive: WHD3: ADD
Endif

If $BOOT EQ "AGS"
  Ex Scripts:Logo
  Ex Scripts:Start_AGS
Endif